            "name": "Arjun Mehta",
            "location": "Delhi",
            "verified": true,
            "product_name": "Kashmiri Acacia Honey 500g"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review": "Ordered for my diabetic mother. The doctor said raw honey is better and this one is exactly what she needed. Packing is beautiful, delivery was in 2 days. Highly recommend!",
            "name": "Sunita Patel",
            "location": "Ahmedabad, Gujarat",
            "verified": true,
            "product_name": "Raw Organic Honey 250g"
          }
        },
        {
          "type": "review",
          "settings": {
            "rating": 5,
            "review": "The gift hamper I ordered for Diwali was a massive hit with my family. Everyone was asking where I got such premium quality honey. The packaging is truly luxury level.",
            "name": "Rohan Nair",
            "location": "Bengaluru, Karnataka",
            "verified": true,
